      • generateNextPartNumber

        public String generateNextPartNumber(String prefix,
                            String delimiter,
                            String suffix)
                              throws DAOException
        Generate the next PartNumber available in the database.
        Parameters:
        prefix - Part number prefix. For example, "JBx".
        delimiter - Character between the prefix and the part number, For example, "_".
        suffix - Example digits, for example "000000" to represent a six digit part number.
        Returns:
        New part umber string, for example "JBx_000001".
        Throws:
        DAOException
